info.author: Dan Watson
info.description: pydmtx is a thin wrapper around libdmtx that reads and writes Data Matrix barcodes as PIL Image objects. Dan Watson wrote the original version of pydmtx in 2006, and allowed it to become a native part of the libdmtx package.
